Equipped Abilities:
 Negative Plane Protection

Special Abilities:
 Blur (thrice per day)
 Imroved Invisibility (thrice per day)
 Improved Haste (thrice per day)

Armor Class Bonus: +2
Saving Throws Bonus: +2
Spell Casting Factor: x2
Fire Resistance Bonus: +50%
Thieving Skills Bonus: +50%

Usable By:
 Nalia~

